## Branching & commits
- **Follow GitFlow:** main, develop, feature/*, release/*, hotfix/*.
- **No direct commits to main or develop.** Create PRs.
- **Commits must follow Conventional Commits** (`feat:`, `fix:`, `docs:`...).
- Always rebase feature branch onto latest develop before PR.

## Pull requests
- PR title = Conventional Commit summarising change scope.
- PR description must reference task ID & DoD.
- Require green CI (lint, tests, build) before merge.

## Versioning & tags
- Use Changesets for semver; no manual version bumps.
- Git tags auto-generated by CI (`vX.Y.Z`).

## Changelogs
- Changesets summary required in PR.
- Do not edit CHANGELOG manually.